title: stranger

description.plain:
In Olivia Rodrigo’s song “stranger,” she beautifully captures the journey of personal growth and moving on from a past relationship. The song’s ultimate message is one of personal strength and the ability to move forward, viewing her ex-partner as a stranger with whom she no longer shares a deep emotional connection.

“stranger” was initially only available on “GUTS (T blue vinyl).” The track was made available again on a Record Store Day exclusive vinyl titled, “GUTS: the secret tracks.” The song was officially released to streaming platforms as part of “GUTS (spilled)” on March 22, 2024.
